casebody.head_matter:
In the Matter of DISCIPLINE OF David E. NEELY.
No. D-2866.
Supreme Court of the United States
Dec. 7, 2015.
David E. Neely, of Chicago, Illinois, is suspended from the practice of law in this Court and a rule will issue, returnable within 40 days, requiring him to show cause why he should not be disbarred from the practice of law in this Court.
